    "start": 844.0,
    "text": "I think I need to go on a serious diet soon."
  },
  {
    "start": 847.0,
    "text": "I want to leave you with three tips."
  },
  {
    "start": 850.0,
    "text": "For next time, you have a custom order here in the US."
  },
  {
    "start": 854.0,
    "text": "Tip number one, be as prepared as possible."
  },
  {
    "start": 859.0,
    "text": "If you're familiar with the menu, that will definitely help things go a bit more smoothly."
  },
  {
    "start": 867.0,
    "text": "So maybe you can research ahead of time and see what the menu is before you go to the restaurant."
  },
  {
    "start": 874.0,
    "text": "Number two, ask questions."
  },
  {
    "start": 877.0,
    "text": "Don't be shy if you don't understand something or you don't know what's on the menu."
  },
  {
    "start": 883.0,
    "text": "You can ask them politely."
  },
  {
    "start": 885.0,
    "text": "You could even explain to them."
  },
  {
    "start": 887.0,
    "text": "It's your first time ordering there or you don't know how it works."
  },
  {
    "start": 892.0,
    "text": "Staff is usually very friendly and helpful."
  },
  {
    "start": 895.0,
    "text": "Don't be embarrassed to ask for help."
  },
  {
    "start": 897.0,
    "text": "And if you don't understand what they say, you can just say something simple like,"
  },
  {
    "start": 902.0,
    "text": "I'm sorry, could you repeat that?"
  },
  {
    "start": 904.0,
    "text": "Or I'm sorry, I didn't catch that."
  },
  {
    "start": 907.0,
    "text": "And they will gladly repeat what they said to you."
  },
  {
    "start": 910.0,
    "text": "Finally, try not to get too anxious or feel too rushed."
  },
  {
    "start": 915.0,
    "text": "My mom and I both said that we also understand that feeling."
  },
  {
    "start": 920.0,
    "text": "Even though we're native English speakers and we've lived in America our whole lives."
  },
  {
    "start": 926.0,
    "text": "So it is completely normal to feel a bit nervous ordering at places like this."
  },
  {
    "start": 932.0,
    "text": "Take your time."
  },
  {
    "start": 933.0,
    "text": "It's okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 934.0,
    "text": "I know these types of restaurants aren't always the easiest place to order,"
  },
  {
    "start": 940.0,
    "text": "but it is an excellent place to practice your English speaking."
  },
  {
    "start": 945.0,
    "text": "So even though it can be a little intimidating, I highly recommend trying it out on your trip to the US."
  },
  {
    "start": 953.0,
    "text": "I hope after watching this video, you feel a bit more confident and comfortable"
  },
  {
    "start": 959.0,
    "text": "to try ordering at restaurants next time you're in the US."
  },
  {
    "start": 963.0,
